Empath raises an eyebrow at the whole tirade.  "Must you boys always 
fall for the new hot chick in town?" she inquires mildly, barely 
sparing a glance for Starstorm.  The ex-Seeker looks to her master.  
<Lord Galvatron,> she says telepathically, <Our avian cohort already 
plots treason.  Personally, I couldn't care less about your reaction 
to Stormy here.  Let her think I'm jealous if she wants.  It's only a 
cover to make Cygnar think I'm looking in the wrong direction.>
